1 “SECTION 8. In adopting rules under section 4 of this 2026 Act, the
2 Environmental Quality Commission shall require that, for a bulk oils
3 or liquid fuels terminal operating in this state on the effective date
4 of this 2026 Act, the initial deadline to apply for a certificate of fi-
5 nancial responsibility be no later than March 31, 2027.”.
6 On page 4, line 1, delete “8” and insert “9”.
7 On page 5, line 7, delete “9” and insert “10”.
